workflows:
    we can bind multiple commands or skills through workflows 
    So plan for having many workflows where a sequential or dependent or indepent parallel multiple tasks to perform.

    You can have ideas of workflows from the archon/.archon/workflows. 
    Just read 5 or 6 random workflows from there just to have sense of syntax/structures. 

    After having full control on workflows, start reasoning on the ai os system where you can have workflows that would make things more advanced and optimized compared to commands and skills. 

    Do deep research on it.

    Then first create an instructive prompt to use workflows in a super manner in the ai os, that would be definitely a discovered work and at least 10x smarter and productive and creative.

    Create a quite large readme on implemention plan for the workflows first. 

    After that i would give feedback and ask you to start building the workflows.  

